E-harem
A large number of potential sexual partners that an [[attention whore|attention]] and/or [[drama whore]] keeps in reserve for times of emotional turbulence, or just when they need to know that they have 10 guys/girls who would fuck him/her in an instant. Scientists believe that this triggers a chemical release that keeps a [[whore]]'s recurring nightmares about being 40 and ugly at bay.

